Introduction

AOA CREAM was a South Korean sub-group of AOA formed by FNC Entertainment. The unit debuted in February 2016 with the single 'I'm Jelly BABY' showcasing superior physical conditions with differentiated charms from AOA's concept. The unit has presumably disbanded following their removal from the agency's website.
